sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Pub as Publisher
    participant EB as EventBus
    participant H1 as exact-type handler
    participant H2 as parent-class handler
    participant AH as async handler

    Note over Pub,EB: Synchronous path: publish()
    Pub->>EB: publish(ContainerUnlockedEvent(...))
    EB->>EB: lock + snapshot handlers
    Note over EB: exact = _handlers[type(event)]<br/>parent = handlers where<br/>isinstance(event, registered_type)

    loop exact handlers
        EB->>H1: handler(event)
        H1-->>EB: return
    end
    loop parent handlers
        EB->>H2: handler(event)
        H2-->>EB: return
    end
    EB-->>Pub: all dispatched

    Note over Pub,EB: Async path: publish_async()
    Pub->>EB: await publish_async(event)
    EB->>EB: publish(event)  (sync pass first)
    EB->>EB: snapshot async handlers
    loop async handlers
        EB->>AH: await handler(event)
        AH-->>EB: return
    end
    EB-->>Pub: complete
